### Test Notification System

# 1. Login as customer
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/customer/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "customer@test.com",
    "password": "password"
}

###

# 2. Get services (copy a service ID for order)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/services

###

